title: Blackstone’s Liftoff Said to Weigh IPO Refile as Soon as Tuesday
description: Liftoff Mobile Inc. filed confidentially for an IPO late Tuesday, less than two weeks after the mobile advertising platform operator postponed plans to raise as much as $762 million.
